`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Spell_Sleep
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * cast sleep <victim>

 This spell puts its victim to sleep. While affected by this spell, you will
not be able to wake yourself, however, once it wears off, you are free to do
so.

